    "en": "The Norwegian Forest Cat is a sweet, loving cat. She appreciates praise and loves to interact with her parent. She makes a loving companion and bonds with her parents once she accepts them for her own. She is still a hunter at heart. She loves to chase toys as if they are real. She is territorial and patrols several times each day to make certain that all is fine.",
    "zh": "挪威森林猫是一种甜美、充满爱意的猫。它欣赏赞美，喜欢与主人互动。一旦它接受主人，就会成为充满爱意的伴侣并与之建立纽带。它内心仍然是一个猎手。它喜欢追逐玩具，仿佛它们是真实的一样。它有领地意识，每天巡逻几次以确保一切正常。"
  },
